reviewText: HAVE 40- REVIEWS ON THE SET ALL THE SAME GREAT
You will have to act fast for so many are made and it is popular that they continue to be sold fast, grab what you can when you can.

I will be buying the whole volume they have out so far.  I fell in love with this show when I visited my mom's house this past June at my homestate.  The show really has a good effect on peoples lives.  Both the young and old.  The show has good family values.  I have never seen a show that has this kind of effect.  There are a lot out there but none has this kind of effect of people.  I hope the series run for a long time.  Although there is the old saying that old good things must also come to an end.  But I along with a lot of people, are not ready for it to end yet.
According to my wife.  Don't want to dissappoint her and it will be a big surprise for our wedding anniversary.  Thank you Amazon.
